dct_title_s: Geodynamic map of the Mediterranean: Sheet 2 - Seismicity and tectonics = Carte geodynamique de la Mediterranee: Feuille 2 - Seismicite et tectonique
dct_description_sm: Commission for the Geological Map of the World. Commission de la carte geologique du monde. North Decimal Degree 52.000000. South Decimal Degree 9.0000. East Decimal Degree 52.0000. West Decimal Degree -12.0000. Mercator projection. Relief shown by shading. Depths shown by gradient tints. Map is accompanied by: Sheet 1. Tectonics and kinematics = feuille 1. Tectonique et cinematique. Published ... with the support of UNESCO, ROMA III, and INVG (Rome)
